events.text: The Shock traded Pierre Berkley, Greg Woodard, Gary Gfeller, Matt Steven, Johan Lacombe, a 2020 2nd round pick (DET), a 2021 2nd round pick (DET), and a 2022 1st round pick (DET) to the Aviators for Zieyik Charles, Rokas Songaila, and Andrew Robinson.
The Shock traded Cale Williams to the Phantoms for Na'Vonta Carter.
The Shock traded nothing to the Aviators for a 2021 2nd round pick (COL).
The Shock traded Jabbar Garcia, a 2020 1st round pick (DET), a 2021 2nd round pick (COL), and a 2022 2nd round pick (DET) to the Kings for Andy Chmielewski and a 2020 1st round pick (BK).
The Shock traded a 2020 1st round pick (BK) to the Kings for nothing.
The Storm traded Mike Canady to the Sabres for Marvin Keely, Troy Augustus, Cameron Williams, and a 2023 1st round pick (KEN).
The Storm traded Richard Auguste and Michael Bedwell to the Scorpions for Jerry McCarter, Antonio Williams, Sean Harris, a 2020 2nd round pick (SEA), and a 2021 2nd round pick (SEA).
The Kings traded Andrew Hunter to the Bolts for Antoine Ejim and a 2021 1st round pick (DAL).
The Kings traded Dallas McLaurin to the Swarm for Bobby Adedeji, a 2020 2nd round pick (CHA), and a 2021 2nd round pick (CHA).
The Gators traded Joel Ellis to the Instinct for Dominique Plater, Reggie Peck, Chris Miller, and a 2020 2nd round pick (IND).
